Package: wickraradar
Type: Package
Title: Data-Driven Liquidation-Cascade Radar Core
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("kingchenc", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@wickra.org")
Description: R bindings for wickra-radar over its C ABI hub: build a Radar from a
    spec JSON, drive it with command JSON and read back a report of alerts - the
    same protocol as the CLI and every other binding.
License: MIT + file LICENSE | Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-radar
BugReports: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-radar/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: the wickra-radar C ABI shared library (WKRADAR_LIB) and its
    header (WKRADAR_INC).
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
